            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%B9%E7%A7%8D%E5%85%B5%E5%BC%8F%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E7%B4%AF%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%B9%E7%A7%8D%E5%85%B5%E5%BC%8F%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E7%B4%AF%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人特种兵式旅游真的不累吗#</span></a> <br><br>利用周末或小长假，用尽可能少的预算，玩最多的景点、吃最多的美食，这种被称为“特种兵式旅游”的游玩方式。<br><br>年轻人有良好的身体素质，能适应快节奏、高消耗，是这种旅游形式走红的原因<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[赢牛奶]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/9c/2021_yingniunai_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>那么问题来了，五一马上到，以你的“身体素质”，能顶得顺一场高消耗的“特种兵式旅游”吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#当代年轻人的身体素质#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6NV3e9Q" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
